# Performance Standards

Performance is luxury.

Target:

60 FPS

Core Web Vitals:

LCP < 2.5s
CLS < 0.1
INP < 200ms

## Rules

Use:

- IntersectionObserver
- requestAnimationFrame

Avoid:

- Heavy scroll listeners
- Layout thrashing
- Re-renders

## React

Use:

React.memo
useMemo
useCallback

When appropriate.

## GPU

Animate only:

transform
opacity

Use:

translate3d(0,0,0)

where needed.
